    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $('Check Decline Criteria').item.json.invitee_email }}",
        "subject": "Thank you for your interest — A gift from Veteran Vectors",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n<p>Hi {{ $('Check Decline Criteria').item.json.invitee_name.split(' ')[0] || 'there' }},</p>\n<p>Thank you so much for taking the time to book a discovery call with Veteran Vectors. We truly appreciate your interest in exploring how automation can transform your business.</p>\n<p>After reviewing the details, it looks like the timing may not be the perfect fit right now — and that's completely okay. We want to make sure that when we work together, we can deliver the maximum value for where your business is at.</p>\n<p>In the meantime, we'd love to share something with you that can help right away:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center; margin: 24px 0;\">\n<a href=\"YOUR_LEAD_MAGNET_URL\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:14px 36px; background:#2c3e50; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; font-size:16px;\">Download Your Free Automation Guide</a>\n</p>\n<p>This guide covers practical automation strategies you can start implementing today, no matter the size of your team.</p>\n<p>When the time is right, we'd love to reconnect. Don't hesitate to reach out — we're always here to help.</p>\n<p>Wishing you continued success,</p>\n<p><strong>The Veteran Vectors Team</strong><br>anthony@veteranvectors.io</p>\n</div>",
        "options": {}
      },
